## Steps to reproduce the issue
Run `read_verilog` for the following reduced case:

```
module scope_issue
 #( parameter n = 16
  )
  (  input [n-1:0] in,
     output [n-1:0] out
  );
  genvar   i;
  generate
    if (1'b1) begin : BLK1
       for ( i = 1;  i <= n - 1; i = i + 1 )  begin : BLK2
         wire [n-1:0] q = in;
         localparam j = i;
         assign out[i] = BLK1.BLK2[i].q[j];
       end
    end
  endgenerate
endmodule

```

